Inatallation steps for using this software.
===========================================

First check your public_html and public_html/cgi-bin is configured or not.
If not then follow below link 
http://satveerkaur.blogspot.in/2012/07/cgi-scripts-execution-using-user.html

After this open terminal and run following commands

1) $ cd public_html/cgi-bin

2) $ git clone https://github.com/GreatDevelopers/bakaplan.git

3) $ cd bakaplan

4) make install

After all above steps open browser and open following link:

http://localhost/~username/BaKaPlan

NOTE:    Be sure that you must have write permission in the directory
         (~/public_html/cgi-bin/bakaplan/ and ~/public_html/)
         where outputfile is to be generated.
